memberdef.name: restore_generator_node
memberdef.initializer: { register CELL *pt_args, *x_args; \ register choiceptr gcp = B; \ /* restore generator choice point */ \ HR = HBREG = PROTECT_FROZEN_H(gcp); \ restore_yaam_reg_cpdepth(gcp); \ CPREG = gcp->cp_cp; \ ENV = gcp->cp_env; \ YAPOR_update_alternative(PREG, (yamop *) AP) \ gcp->cp_ap = (yamop *) AP; \ /* restore args */ \ pt_args = (CELL *)(GEN_CP(gcp) + 1) + ARITY; \ x_args = XREGS + 1 + ARITY; \ while (x_args > XREGS + 1) { \ register CELL x = pt_args[-1]; \ --x_args; \ --pt_args; \ *x_args = x; \ } \ }

memberdef.name: pop_generator_node
memberdef.initializer: { register CELL *pt_args, *x_args; \ register choiceptr gcp = B; \ /* pop generator choice point */ \ HR = PROTECT_FROZEN_H(gcp); \ pop_yaam_reg_cpdepth(gcp); \ CPREG = gcp->cp_cp; \ ENV = gcp->cp_env; \ TR = gcp->cp_tr; \ B = gcp->cp_b; \ HBREG = PROTECT_FROZEN_H(B); \ /* pop args */ \ x_args = XREGS + 1 ; \ pt_args = (CELL *)(GEN_CP(gcp) + 1); \ while (x_args < XREGS + 1 + ARITY) { \ register CELL x = pt_args[0]; \ pt_args++; \ x_args++; \ x_args[-1] = x; \ } \ YENV = pt_args; \ SET_BB(PROTECT_FROZEN_B(B)); \ }

memberdef.name: store_consumer_node
memberdef.initializer: { register choiceptr ccp; \ register dep_fr_ptr new_dep_fr; \ /* initialize ccp */ \ YENV = (CELL *) (CONS_CP(YENV) - 1); \ ccp = NORM_CP(YENV); \ /* adjust freeze registers */ \ H_FZ = HR; \ B_FZ = ccp; \ TR_FZ = TR; \ /* store dependency frame */ \ new_dependency_frame(new_dep_fr, DEP_ON_STACK, LOCAL_top_or_fr, \ LEADER_CP, ccp, SG_FR, FALSE, LOCAL_top_dep_fr); \ LOCAL_top_dep_fr = new_dep_fr; \ /* store consumer choice point */ \ HBREG = HR; \ store_yaam_reg_cpdepth(ccp); \ ccp->cp_tr = TR; \ ccp->cp_ap = ANSWER_RESOLUTION; \ ccp->cp_h = HR; \ ccp->cp_b = B; \ ccp->cp_env= ENV; \ ccp->cp_cp = CPREG; \ CONS_CP(ccp)->cp_dep_fr = LOCAL_top_dep_fr; \ store_low_level_trace_info(CONS_CP(ccp), TAB_ENT); \ /* set_cut((CELL *)ccp, B); --> no effect */ \ B = ccp; \ YAPOR_SET_LOAD(B); \ SET_BB(B); \ TABLING_ERROR_CHECKING_STACK; \ }
